{"tid":242382,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人用過國泰大專生個個機票優惠","createTime":"2017-05-14T00:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T08:57:43.000Z","uid":72741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7a4d99a59b17a3b62163ed8b21d8bad1118fb54","tid":242382,"uid":72741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T00:43:27.000Z","msg":"我買個時係用屋企人張信用卡 但confirm email入面有行係 <br />\n持卡人必須於辦理登機手續時出示支付機票的信用卡以供核實。此外，持卡人亦可於航班出發前在國泰航空票務辦事處出示有關信用卡以供核實。若持卡人未能出示用作預訂交易的信用卡，航空公司保留拒絕登機或收取保證付款之權利。<br />\n<br />\n有無人試過真係比人要求出示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係就要勞煩我老豆去票務處搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da40253c7cd930cec59974135bdf85b1cc55a7ce","tid":242382,"uid":6213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T00:51:21.000Z","msg":"用過一次<br />\n記憶中無要求出示信用卡<br />\n學生證就要"},{"pid":"63da5cc255457e056c47ee6d316de7bda49c35fc","tid":242382,"uid":93640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:02:41.000Z","msg":"未奶過野，但唔好搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n快d出返張卡啦，去外地冇信用卡應急都好麻煩下"},{"pid":"7c63446cdd369581af7b99d276a0b66f1a394ba0","tid":242382,"uid":16732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:07:25.000Z","msg":"影印副本再簽返名我諗都得嘅<br />\n之前我幫人買 hkexpree好似要信用卡本人 即係我既身份證同信用卡副本再簽個名就ok"},{"pid":"79d7083e2315d9edb80fe3644914886f2e42fbb1","tid":242382,"uid":33703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:34:49.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係學生飛<br />\n之前喺官網用自己卡買 checkin比佢問攞張卡黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08a1d4fdfff91cc32f4c260fa18cb75a9480738","tid":242382,"uid":72741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:44:09.000Z","msg":"咁真係睇彩數佢會唔會叫你比張卡佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c187157a29b0cbf1cce788f57a55df3b0992562a","tid":242382,"uid":32899,"like":0,